name: RPG
body:
MMORPG ===================== About ------------ A fast and real time open source MMORPG demo. Developed in HTML 5, JavaScript and web sockets. Features ------------ -Multiplayer functionality.
-Cross browser.
-Real time player movement.
-Zelda-like battle system.
-Events and enemies artificial intelligence (AI).
-Character selection.
-Map editor.
